  "Jayshree Ullal has been president and CEO of Arista Networks, a computer networking firm, since 2008.",
  "The publicly-traded company recorded revenues of $2.2 billion in 2018.",
  "Ullal owns about 5% of Arista's stock, some of which is earmarked for her two children, niece and nephew.",
  "In August 2018, Arista settled a multi-year patent infringement battle with Cisco, Ullal's former employer, agreeing to pay Cisco $400 million. \r\n\r\n",
  "Born in London and raised in India, she is now one of America's wealthiest female executives."
